classes.name: _NumpyPlugin
classes.docstring: A mypy plugin for handling versus numpy-specific typing tasks.

methods.name: get_type_analyze_hook
methods.docstring:
Set the precision of platform-specific `numpy.number`
subclasses.

For example: `numpy.int_`, `numpy.longlong` and `numpy.longdouble`.

methods.name: get_additional_deps
methods.docstring:
Handle all import-based overrides.

* Import platform-specific extended-precision `numpy.number`
  subclasses (*e.g.* `numpy.float96`, `numpy.float128` and
  `numpy.complex256`).
* Import the appropriate `ctypes` equivalent to `numpy.intp`.
